change the bucket num compute method in bucket shuffle join

When plan bucket shuffle join, we need to know left table bucket number.
Currently, we use tablet number directly based on the assumption that left table has only one partition.

body:
origin _levels is between size_based_compaction_lower_bound_size and
size_based_promotion_size, default conf is 64M and 1024M, which is too
big for cu compaction, and once rowset size bigger than 64M it will be
promoted to base, so this rule seems to be useless.

update _leves to between 32M and 1K, which will reduce a lot of cpu.
In our test, we have 20 concurrent stream load and each rowset in disk
is 3K, after introduce this change, we save about 25% cpu.
